Package org.aksw.iguana.rp.storage.impl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileStorage
    This Storage will save the results in the following directory structure
    SuiteID/ExperimentID/Experiment Extra Meta HashCode/Metric Short Name/

    The file Names will be
    1.
    FileStorageTest
    Will test The FileStorage directory structure and the content of the csv files
    NTFileStorage
    Will save results as NTriple File
    NTFileStorageTest
    This will test the NTFileStorage in short.
    PropertiesSenderStorage
    Will provide all the results as Properties and will send them to a rabbit queue
    The rabbit queue can be defined by the constructor.
    PropertiesSenderStorageTest
    Will check if the Properties will be sended via rabbitMQ
    TriplestoreStorage
    This Storage will save all the metric results into a specified triple store
    TriplestoreStorageTest
    Will test if the TriplestoreStorage sends the correct INSERT command to a Mock Server
